data.description: Country Living, with many amnesties near by 1408 SQFT 3 bed 2bath   manufactured home located 30 miles south of Downtown San Antonio. In Devine Texas. Interior, has open floorplan, kitchen with plenty of cabinet storage space, a dishwasher, and refrigerator. The one and a half acre property is fenced with 2x4 field fence, anchored by 12 inch posts. Master bath has both a stand in shower and a bathtub. The tub was never connected to water source. The property is dotted with a variety of 8 year old shade trees. Property also has a 30x20 two car detached carport, and two 30x15 covered patios.
